metadata.description:
Float #01 

Float is a photo series I used to cope with C-PTSD. 

One way to manage panic and anxiety is to ground yourself. This series was a way to reclaim feeling safe. When everything feels dangerous.

This spacesuit will be upgraded and never again replicated.

1/1
5000 x 5000
Panasonic GH5
